description:
JazzTimes In Person interview with pianist, composer and bandleader Michel Camilo from backstage at the 2011 Newport Jazz Festival, presented by Natixis.  In this segment, Camilo talks about playing at Newport with his new trio and about the challenges of playing solo piano.

This segment is one of several done with Camilo and other musicians who were performing at the Newport Jazz Festival.

Interview by Lee Mergner. Video by Melissa Mergner.

For more information about JazzTimes magazine, go to jazztimes.com.
